报"},"attached_info":"CkII3rSJ46PmuKwuEAMaCTExMjk4MTQ5MyCqiLS8BjAAOOwDQBRyCzEwMDI3MjQ1ODc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e9592b88b82b66c38a23d9736ac39db_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1737354257.788147","card_id":"Q_5659322941","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5659322941,"title":"所谓“无锁数据结构”，是不是可以理解为本质上并不是“无锁”，而只是锁定粒度降到了最低？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5659322941","type":"question","created":1733052267,"answer_count":15,"follower_count":76,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[13849],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我认为原子量实质上是一种最低粒度的“锁”——它只能保护机器字范围数据的互斥访问。从这一角度理解，所谓无锁数据结构里并不是完全没有锁了，只是锁的粒度足够细，充分挖掘了数据结构内部的无关性。 原子量能够用来实现自旋锁等“大锁”，是不是也可以证明原子量本身也是一种锁？ 因此，“真正无锁”的数据结构就是那些完全分布式的，彼此之间没有任何共享状态，纯粹依靠传值的消息通讯的结构，也就是分布式系统。因为没有任何瓜葛，各部分完全毫无顾忌地尽情并发处理。"},"attached_info":"CkAI3rSJ46PmuKwuEAMaCTExMjEwODQ0MCDrjrG6BjAAOExAFXIKNTY1OTMyMjk0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1737354257.788697","card_id":"Q_661040885","target":{"id":661040885,"title":"河南哪里的胡辣汤最正宗呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661040885","type":"question","created":1720413461,"answer_count":52,"follower_count":62,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5483,169424,2228168],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I3rSJ46PmuKwuEAMaCTEwOT